column1: ##DESCRIPTION=cnv_type=Type of CNV: focal (< 25 % of chrom. arm, < 3 genes), cluster (focal, > 3 genes), (partial) p/q-arm, (partial) chromosome.
##DESCRIPTION=CGI_genes=Genes which were included in CancerGenomeInterpreter.org analysis.
##DESCRIPTION=CGI_driver_statement=Driver statement for cancer type NS according CancerGenomeInterpreter.org
##DESCRIPTION=CGI_gene_role=Gene role for cancer type NS according CancerGenomeInterpreter.org
##DESCRIPTION=ncg_oncogene=1:gene is oncogene according NCG6.0, 0:No oncogene according NCG6.0, na: no information available about gene in NCG6.0. Order is the same as in column CGI_genes.
##DESCRIPTION=ncg_tsg=1:gene is TSG according NCG6.0, 0:No TSG according NCG6.0, na: no information available about gene in NCG6.0. Order is the same as in column CGI_genes.
